{"id":106235,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/富人喜欢邓小平，穷人怀念毛泽东/","date":"2010-09-21T01:06:51Z","modified":"2010-09-28T05:46:04Z","title":"富人喜欢邓小平，穷人怀念毛泽东?","content":"<p><p align=\"left\"><span>自从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1994</span><span>年春节以后，邓小平就再也没有公开露面。境外的媒体至少一百次说他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>病危</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>，他却在京城里自己那个四方形的院落中，过得既舒适又洒脱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1996</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月的一个清晨，邓小平住进北京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">301</span><span>医院；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1997</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月，医院的报告说邓小平病危。据医生黄琳说，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>我能体会他临终前还是比较痛苦的，但一声不吭</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>；无论昏睡还是清醒，都不说话，他已经不再评价别人，也不再在意别人的评价。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span>黄琳曾问他还有什么话想说，总该再给中国人留点什么吧？可是邓小平淡淡地回答：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>该说的都说过了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日，他的呼吸功能都衰竭，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>分，邓小平的心脏停止了跳动。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>该说的都说过了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>，成为邓小平的临终遗言。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>年后，在<span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>月份， ……</p>\n<p>……</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><strong><span><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span><span></p>\n<p><span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>\n</p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[9091,10951]}